textRun.content: This document tests the importer's ability to handle multiple languages and encodings within a single document. It includes content in English, French, Spanish, Japanese, and Arabic. The importer must preserve text direction, special characters, and Unicode formatting accurately.
Hello! This is an English paragraph meant to validate basic Latin character import.
Bonjour ! Ceci est un paragraphe en français pour valider l'importation des caractères accentués et spéciaux.
¡Hola! Este es un párrafo en español con signos de exclamación invertidos y caracteres como ñ y á.
こんにちは！これは日本語の段落で、インポート時にUnicodeの正確性を確認するためのテストです。
مرحبًا! هذه فقرة باللغة العربية للتحقق من دعم النص من اليمين إلى اليسار أثناء الاستيراد.
This paragraph mixes languages: Bonjour, this is an English-French hybrid. ¡Hola! こんにちは! مرحبًا! Each script should maintain its formatting and display correctly.

All multilingual content should appear correctly encoded and displayed. The importer must support both left-to-right and right-to-left scripts without data loss, ensuring that accented characters and Unicode text are preserved.
